---
title: Seared Chicken & Creamy Onion Sauce with Steamed Green Beans & Veggie Mash
description: There’s only one soulmate sauce for a tender chicken and that’s a white sauce. Add some onion to this creamy dream
and drizzle it over to serve beside a cheerful veggie mash of potato and carrot.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

